=== Etymology ===
: From the Venetian dialectical pronunciation of ''[[schiavo]]'' meaning (I'm your) ''[[slave]]'', pronouced in "s-ciao". In other words, the greeting started by saying ''I am your humble slave'', similar to the Central European greeting of ''[[servus]]''.